  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Both definitions of “Hope” are sourced from <strong>Webster’s Dictionary 1828</strong> which lives online at <a href="https://www.webstersdictionary1828.com" class="note-highlight">webstersdictionary1828.com</a>.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

